SEC power poll: Ole Miss puts unbeaten start on line against Gators 
By Don Coble Thu, Oct 1, 2015 @ 10:06 pm | updated Thu, Oct 1, 2015 @ 10:10 pm Photos AP FILE - In this Sept. 19, 2015, file photo, Mississippi quarterback Chad Kelly dives in for a touchdown past Alabama linebacker Shaun Hamilton during first half of an NCAA college football game in Tuscaloosa, Ala. After leading East Mississippi Community College to a national title, Kelly transferred to Ole Miss, where he is ranked second nationally in passing efficiency.
